User système: squash-tm

COMMANDES UTILES
----------------
Statut du service:
  sudo systemctl status squash-tm

Redémarrer:
  sudo systemctl restart squash-tm

Logs:
  sudo journalctl -u squash-tm -f
  tail -f {{ install_dir }}/logs/squash-tm.log

Arrêter:
  sudo systemctl stop squash-tm

